Package: cliphist
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         wl-clipboard,
         xdg-utils
Description: Wayland clipboard manager with text and image support
 cliphist is a clipboard manager for Wayland that stores both text and
 image data. It integrates with wl-clipboard to provide clipboard history
 that persists across sessions.
 .
 Features include:
  - Store text and image clipboard data
  - Persistent clipboard history
  - Integration with rofi, dmenu, or other launchers
  - Lightweight and fast
  - Perfect for Wayland compositors
